results.description: Captain America is back and he must save Sharon Carter from certain death!

textObjects.text: Captain America is back and he must save Sharon Carter from certain death!

Amid a background of destruction and rubble, Captain America stands alone holding the American flag for all to see.  Ron Garney effortlessly creates a stoic and patriotic image of the star-spangled Avenger that captures the valor and spirit of the hero.  No small feat.  Cap, we salute you.
